              <h2>About This Site</h2>
              <p>This site serves as a personal playground for development experiments and a portfolio of projects. Built with a retro Windows 95/98 aesthetic because nostalgia meets functionality.</p>
              <p>The design features both light (mint green) and dark (terminal green) themes - toggle using the button in the menu bar!</p>
              <h3>What You'll Find Here</h3>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Posts</strong> - Project updates, tutorials, and tech explorations</li>
                <li><strong>Code Experiments</strong> - Trying out new technologies and approaches</li>
                <li><strong>Documentation</strong> - Notes and learnings from the development journey</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
